contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|international}} '''[[International]]''' is an adjective (also used as a noun) meaning "between nations". '''International''' may also refer to: * International, California, former name of [[Walkermine, California]] * [[International (train)|''International'' (train)]], a Great Northern service * ''[[International Limited]]'', a Canadian National & Grand Trunk Western service * [[International Paint|International]], the [[AkzoNobel]] business unit Marine and Protective Coating brand * [[International (New Order album)|''International'' (New Order album)]], 2002 * [[International (The Three Degrees album)|''International'' (The Three Degrees album)]], 1975 * [[International (Kevin Michael album)|''International'' (Kevin Michael album)]], 2011 * [[International Harvester]], a predecessor of Navistar International * [[Navistar International]], an Illinois truck manufacturer * [[WTA International tournaments]], tournaments of the Women's Tennis Association * a former name of the [[Scottish Open (snooker)]], a professional snooker tournament * a former name of [[Molde FK]], Norwegian association football club * [[Political international]], any of several international political associations * [[International (steamship)|''International'']], steamship seized [[Louis Riel]] == See also == * [[The International (disambiguation)]] * [[International style (disambiguation)]] * [[Multinational (disambiguation)]] * [[Transnational (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}}
